window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>In <i>Ninja Innovation,</i> Gary Shapiro, the head of the Consumer Electronics Association, answers the universal question - What leads to success? - revealing how everyone can use the ninja way to create a killer strategy that will help them achieve their own goals. \"Ninja Innovation\" is his ultimate how-to for envisioning, executing, and maintaining a successful innovation-based strategy like those utilized in the technology world.</p>"; 
